Write a poem about AI with exactly 50 words
In the future, humans will be able to live longer and healthier lives. What do you think are some of the main reasons for this?
Humans have been given an extended lease on life thanks to advancements in medicine and technology. The ability to analyze genes has led to personalized treatments that fight diseases more effectively, while AI-powered robots perform surgeries with greater precision than ever before. With the help of these tools, people can live longer, healthier lives.
